      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make sure the essay doesn't just sound like it's presenting one side. how should i address the counter-arguments? like, people always bring up meritocracy and say it's unfair to take from those who worked hard. how can i frame those arguments so they don't undermine the main point of my essay?",
